        <h2 class="marketing-columns">{{#link-to 'artist.bose'}}Subarna Talukder Bose{{/link-to}}</h2>
        <p>Subarna Talukder Bose is exhibiting paintings at Red Fox Bar in April 2018.</p>
        <p>Subarna is originally from Calcutta, India. She has recently exhibited her art in various exhibitions across Corvallis. Before coming to US in 2015 she worked as a journalist in India for five years. She holds a BA in English Literature and a PG Dip in Journalism. She volunteers at Corvallis Arts Center and OSU Folk Club.</p>
