        <h2 class="marketing-columns">{{#link-to 'group.akasu-winter2018'}}Berlin, Kruse, Reeves, Schneider, Wolf at Akasu Hair Studio and Spa{{/link-to}}</h2>
        <p>This is Verge's first exhibition at Akasu Salon. Jason Berlin and Veronica Reeves are showing paintings on the first floor. Rachel Wolf, Brandi ruse, and Harry Schneider are showing prints upstairs.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
